  "text": "\u2022 R Li : reliability of link L i between nodes n i and n i+1 a) Unipath route reliability: Route reliability between a source n 0 and a destination n m composed of m links and (m + 1) nodes is equal product of reliability of all links and nodes on this route [CITATION_1] :",
